  <description><![CDATA[<p>A superb slope-side complex offering classic, yet modern hotel rooms in perfect ski - in/ski - out position and located at the Peak Nine base</p>
<p>Hotel offers all the daily amenities one would require for a holiday with choice of restaurants and bars and shops.</p>
<p>Beaver Run Resort has Unique indoor/outdoor pool, seven mountain view hot tubs, spa with sauna and steam room and fitness room.</p>
<p>From the base of Peak Nine you can take the High speed Quad chairlift.</p>]]></description>
